### Skills Across Loops

Skills are shared through `{shared_dir}/skills/`. Treat them as reusable tools and workflows.

- **work_loop:** read and use existing skills when they help the current plan. You may create a small draft skill or helper script while exploring if it directly supports the current eval, but keep the notebook as the main work memory.
- **reflect_loop:** after a successful real eval, promote what was actually validated into a durable skill. Create or update a skill only when the technique, script, diagnostic, or workflow is reusable in later work.

